case.title: Fit Indian guy seeks woman - 36 (London Berkshire)
case.text:
Hello
I am a fit Indian guy who is looking for a genuine woman. I like sport and go swimming and gym 3 times a week. I am in a complicated relationship and am looking for a companion. You too may be in a similar situation. Please send your pictures and phone number. I live in west London. Please note NO money exchange either side. Looking for genuine woman.
